    <string name="whats_new">Welcome to DashTracker!
        \n\nThis update brings automatic mileage tracking to the app. Starting a new dash has been
        simplified—when you\'re ready to start your dash, just press the start button, enter your
        starting mileage and DashTracker takes care of the rest for you. When your dash is over,
        verify the mileage is correct and enter your earnings.
        \n\nAutomatic mileage tracking requires some permissions to work, so if you\'d like to take
        advantage of its benefits, select "Enable" below. If you\'d prefer not to use automatic
        mileage tracking, select "Decline," and you can continue to enter start and end odometer
        values manually. You can always switch at any time by going to settings.</string>
